mail <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">users</ENAMEX>[.]" 39
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">U.S.C.</ENAMEX> ¬<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">ß 403</NUMEX>(b)(<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">2</ENAMEX>).
The <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Reorganization Act</ENAMEX> grants the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Postal Service</ENAMEX> specific powers
