recommendations. The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Commission</ENAMEX> conducted a rulemaking to consider
the rules proposed in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Service</ENAMEX>'s petition, and after considering
the comments of interested <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">parties</ENAMEX>, implemented <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</NUMEX> of the
proposed initiatives, albeit in revised form.
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Three</NUMEX> of the new sets of rules prescribe expedited procedures
